source:
TEXT_BANKJN604_03000_SEQ_00<tab>Zukin is a Kojin with a new purpose for old chests.

※Please note that the difficulty of this quest has been synced to your current level. Furthermore, you may not proceed with a class or job that is different from when you accepted this quest.
target:
TEXT_BANKJN604_03000_SEQ_00<tab><var 48 F201FC /var><var 49 F201FD /var>特殊ルール： レベルアジャスト受注クラス・ジョブ制限<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>
※本クエストは受注時のクラス・ジョブでのみ進行します。

碧のタマミズのズキンは、大物を狙っているようだ。

source: TEXT_BANKJN604_03000_TODO_00<tab>Inspect octopus traps near the <var 1A 02 /var>Adventure<var 1A 01 /var> and obtain an octopus.
target:
TEXT_BANKJN604_03000_TODO_00<tab>海中のアドヴェンチャー号周辺で<var 28 ((EObj)) F61EA83A01 /var>を調べ
<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E8DF701 /var>を入手

source: TEXT_BANKJN604_03000_TODO_01<tab>Deliver the giant koromo octopus to Zukin.

TEXT_BANKJN604_03000_ZUKIN_000_000<tab>We had some old treasure chests that were lying around, gathering dust. With some creativity on my part, I was able to convert them into octopus traps. And they work exceptionally well, if I may say so myself.
target:
TEXT_BANKJN604_03000_ZUKIN_000_000<tab><var 08 E905 ((姉)) ((兄)) /var>さん、聞いてくれぇ～！
用済みになった宝箱が、もったいねぇから、
少し手を加えて、タコを獲るための罠にしたんだぁ～！

source: TEXT_BANKJN604_03000_ZUKIN_000_001<tab>Now, I've a mind to gift the good folk of Kokajiya with a fresh catch, and I should be grateful if you could go out and inspect the traps.
target:
TEXT_BANKJN604_03000_ZUKIN_000_001<tab>これがまた、よく獲れるってんで、
余ったタコを、小鍛冶屋に届けようと思ってんだぁ～。
<var 08 E905 ((姉)) ((兄)) /var>さん、ちょっと仕掛けた罠を見てきてくれぇ～。

source: TEXT_BANKJN604_03000_ZUKIN_000_002<tab>I've laid three over by the wreck southwest of here. One is bound to have caught an octopus by now. My thanks in advance, <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>.
target:
TEXT_BANKJN604_03000_ZUKIN_000_002<tab>「<var 28 ((EObj)) F61EA83A01 /var>」は、南西の海に3つ仕掛けてあるぜぇ～。
そん中のどれかには、「<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E8DF701 /var>」がかかってるはずだから、
回収してきてくれぇ～！

TEXT_BANKJN604_03000_SYSTEM_000_010<tab>この宝箱には、<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E8DF701 /var>はいないようだ……。
ほかの宝箱を調べよう。

source: TEXT_BANKJN604_03000_SYSTEM_000_011<tab>There is a mess of writhing tentacles in the chest!
target: TEXT_BANKJN604_03000_SYSTEM_000_011<tab>宝箱を調べると、<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E8DF701 /var>がかかっていた！

source: TEXT_BANKJN604_03000_ZUKIN_000_020<tab>Ah, there you are. Did the kami bless us with a catch?
target:
TEXT_BANKJN604_03000_ZUKIN_000_020<tab><var 08 E905 ((姉)) ((兄)) /var>さん、戻ってきたなぁ～！
<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E8DF701 /var>は、獲れたかぁ～？

source: TEXT_BANKJN604_03000_ZUKIN_000_021<tab>Oho, such a large and lively octopus! Our blacksmith friends shall be pleased!
target:
TEXT_BANKJN604_03000_ZUKIN_000_021<tab>おぉ～、こりゃあ活きがいいタコだぜぇ～！
これだけ大きけりゃぁ、小鍛冶屋のヒトたちも喜ぶぞぉ～！

source: TEXT_BANKJN604_03000_ZUKIN_000_023<tab>By the way, did I mention that older chests wreathed in weeds make the best traps? Well, they do. You may wish to remember this for your future reference.
target:
TEXT_BANKJN604_03000_ZUKIN_000_023<tab>そういえば、古くて藻の生えたような宝箱のほうが、
<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E8DF701 /var>がかかりやすいって聞いたぞぉ～。
また頼むかもしれないから、覚えておいてくれぇ～！
